### Fazer login para obter token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "casamento123"
}

### Variável para armazenar o token (substitua pelo token obtido no login)
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ========== ROTAS ADMINISTRATIVAS DE GRUPOS ==========

### Listar todos os grupos
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar novo grupo
POST http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Família Silva"
}

### Buscar grupo por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/groups/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar grupo
PUT http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/groups/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Família Silva Santos"
}

### Deletar grupo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/groups/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== ROTAS ADMINISTRATIVAS DE CONVIDADOS ==========

### Listar todos os convidados
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar convidados confirmados
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin?confirmed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar convidados de um grupo específico
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin?groupId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar novo convidado
POST http://localhost:3000/guests/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "isChild": false,
  "groupId": 1
}

### Criar convidado sem grupo
POST http://localhost:3000/guests/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Santos",
  "isChild": false
}

### Buscar convidado por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar convidado
PUT http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva Santos",
  "confirmed": true,
  "isChild": false,
  "groupId": 2
}

### Confirmar convidado
PUT http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirmed": true
}

### Deletar convidado
DELETE http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Estatísticas dos convidados
GET http://localhost:3000/guests/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

